---
import { Plus, Minus } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Get answers to common questions about solar PV design, installation requirements, and our CAD services
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              What information do you need to design my solar PV system?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We need your property's electrical usage history, roof dimensions and orientation, local utility requirements, 
            and any shading constraints. Our team will also analyze your site's solar irradiance and local building codes 
            to create the optimal system design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              How do you optimize panel placement for maximum energy production?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our optimization process considers sun path analysis, roof tilt and orientation, potential shading from 
            nearby structures, and local weather patterns. We use advanced software to model different configurations 
            and select the layout that maximizes annual energy production.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              What electrical codes and standards do your designs meet?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <div class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>All our solar PV designs comply with the National Electrical Code (NEC) Article 690, local electrical codes, 
            and utility interconnection requirements.</p>
            <p>We also ensure compliance with IEEE 1547 standards for grid-connected systems and UL listing requirements 
            for all specified equipment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              Can you design systems with battery storage integration?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we design solar systems with provisions for current or future battery storage integration. Our designs 
            include AC or DC coupling options, backup circuit selection, and smart energy management systems for 
            optimal battery utilization and grid interaction.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              What CAD deliverables do you provide?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <div class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>Our comprehensive CAD package includes detailed panel layout drawings, electrical single-line diagrams, 
            DC and AC wiring schematics, and 3D system visualizations.</p>
            <p>All drawings are permit-ready and include equipment specifications, performance calculations, 
            and compliance documentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              How long does the design process take?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Typical residential systems take 3-5 business days for complete design and documentation. 
            Commercial and industrial projects may require 1-2 weeks depending on complexity. We provide 
            regular updates throughout the process and accommodate rush orders when needed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              Do you provide ongoing support after design completion?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we provide comprehensive post-design support including permit assistance, installer coordination, 
            design revisions if needed, and technical support during installation. Our team remains available 
            throughout your project completion.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-900 to-indigo-900 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Start Your Solar Project?</h3>
        <p class="text-yellow-100 mb-6">Our solar experts are ready to design the perfect PV system for your needs</p>
        <a href="/contact?#contact-form" class="bg-white text-orange-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-300 inline-block">
          Start Your Project
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Add FAQ toggle functionality
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqButtons = document.querySelectorAll('section button');
    
    faqButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', function(event: Event) {
        const target = event.currentTarget as HTMLElement;
        const content = target.nextElementSibling as HTMLElement;
        const icon = target.querySelector('svg');
        
        if (content.style.display === 'none' || content.style.display === '') {
          content.style.display = 'block';
          icon?.classList.remove('lucide-plus');
          icon?.classList.add('lucide-minus');
        } else {
          content.style.display = 'none';
          icon?.classList.remove('lucide-minus');
          icon?.classList.add('lucide-plus');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>